data.description: Custom Multi-generational home w/ panoramic views! Quiet private oasis in Meadow Ranch w/ 3 separate living areas on 2+ acres! Main level w/gorgeous wood flooring & vaulted ceilings, spacious living room w/ wet bar & formal dining. Separate great room is perfect to relax after a long day & enjoymountain views. Kitchen w/ granite counters, island & multiple wall ovens for the at home chef! Owner's suite w/ private outdoor access & jetted tub! Main level 4bed+ office/ 2.5 baths. Lower level w/ wet bar & game room to entertain guests! Tile flooring throughout & private patio to enjoy endless views! Lower level 4 bed/2 baths. Bonus 2 bed/ 1 bath apartment is perfect for renting out! Attached 3-car & detached 4 car garages w/ ½ bath. Income potential is endless.
